        "Invert the constitutive relation P = ПҮ(T)ОөвӮҖE to get E = P/(ПҮ(T)ОөвӮҖ) = PT/(nKОөвӮҖ)",
        "Compute (вҲӮE/вҲӮT)_p = (вҲӮE/вҲӮT)_P = P/(nKОөвӮҖ) by differentiating E = PT/(nKОөвӮҖ) at fixed p (equivalently fixed P since V is constant)"
