      "Cross-check by analogy: for an ideal gas (вҲӮU/вҲӮV)_T = -T(вҲӮP/вҲӮT)_V + P = -TВ·(nk) + nkT = 0 вҖ” the same cancellation structure confirms the Curie-law dielectric is the electromagnetic analogue of the ideal gas"
    ]
